 <summary>Reverse Proxy (web accelerator) PHP compatibility layer</summary>
 <description>Makes reverse-proxing (web accelerator) totally invisible for php applications. Doesn&apos;t require php code modifications to handle X-Forwarded-IP.
* Stills allows proxy-aware applications to work with X-Forwarded headers and proxy IP address.
* Should work with any web server
* Should work with any proxy server

Using this extension with on a non reverse proxied system will result in a security issue.</description>
